 Corpus Name: CCMatrix
     Package: CCMatrix.bn-en in Moses format
     Website: http://opus.nlpl.eu/CCMatrix-v1.php
     Release: v1
Release date: Fri Jun 11 17:40:55 EEST 2021

This corpus is part of OPUS - the open collection of parallel corpora
OPUS Website: http://opus.nlpl.eu


This corpus has been extracted from web crawls using the margin-based bitext mining techniques described at https://github.com/facebookresearch/LASER/tree/master/tasks/CCMatrix.
Please, cite the following papers:
 * Holger Schwenk, Guillaume Wenzek, Sergey Edunov, Edouard Grave, Armand Joulin and Angela Fan, CCMatrix: Mining Billions of High-Quality Parallel Sentences on the WEB (https://arxiv.org/abs/1911.04944),
